{"tid":1575210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港國歌] 唔好將「願榮光歸香港」譯做其他語言","createTime":"2019-09-16T17:52:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T07:01:29.000Z","uid":151256,"like":96,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"84037453e02662290e20abebf053bd6770fbe7e2","tid":1575210,"uid":151256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T17:52:29.000Z","msg":"事緣今日睇到立場post咗「願榮光歸香港」嘅日文版本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你覺得呢首歌係莊嚴同要做國歌嘅，可唔可唔好將佢整做多國語言版？ <br />\n<br />\n呢首歌唔係撐起雨傘同今天我呢啲流行曲，呢首歌嘅地位係國歌呀！要唱就唱返原版！<br />\n<br />\n外國朋友聽唔明嘅話，<span style=\"color: red;\">加字幕可以，但唔好改詞。  <br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n你有無見過其他國歌嘅國歌會有外語版？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好自己走去downgrade 首國歌，唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a867219143ea3a804787bbbadb9b1a0d0d4a7ca2","tid":1575210,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T17:53:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvsTHEi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpvsTHEi.jpg&h=e8bfe3ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">星期三有大綱睇</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">宣佈 和你suck 4.0 9月22 星期日見<br />\n<br />\nsuck 4.0 將會基於 hkmap.live 行動  <br />\n麻煩力推呢個livemap <br />\n對各位日後行動都非常大幫助<br />\n<br />\n請各位必須係 9月22日當日12點30分留意channel / 連登 / IG 最新消息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568754</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n TG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rcWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=0b5dbcf4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\nIG : <a href=\"https://instagram.com/suck.withyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fsuck.withyou&d=CoE